OL,2,MRepair Cafés: Come for the Soldering,
OL,4,MStay for the Stories
OL,6,CAdam Bradley
OL,7,CSat 10:40-11:10
OL,8,CStage A
OL,10,GWhat is a Repair Café and why should
OL,11,Gyou take part in one? Fighting against
OL,12,Gthe throwaway society, Repair Cafes
OL,13,Gbring together local people with
OL,14,Gbroken or worn items and volunteer
OL,15,Gfixers with the skills to repair them.
OL,16,GWe fix things like clothes, furniture,
OL,17,Gappliances, electronics and toys. If
OL,18,Gyou’re a maker at EMF then your skills
OL,19,Gwith a soldering iron could be
OL,20,Gvaluable - or so you’d think. But
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
